      "FacilityID": 38777,
      "SummaryText": "Cerveceria India, Inc. is an established brewery in Mayaguez, PR, with 280 employees.  In the course of producing beverages, Cerveceria India uses one of the compounds which appear on the list of Risk Management Planning chemicals and which is stored in greater-than-threshold quantities.  Specifically, at the refrigeration system, ammonia is utilized in a closed system.  This system is essential for the manufacture of beverages at the facility.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           *Prevention Program: Cerveceria India, Inc., has implemented a prevention program for the covered process.  Hazard reviews have been conducted, and updated at least every five years to aid in identifying hazards and recommendations for improvement.  Operators and maintenance personnel are trained and provided with written instructions as well as safe work practices.  Training is provided at least every three years or more often if necessary.  Contractors working in or adjacent to the refrigeration system receive training in applicable ammonial hazards and safe work practices.  Cerveceria India, Inc. has developed procedures for maintaining the ongoing integrity of equipment.  Compliance audits have been conducted at least every three years, and recommendations addressed continuously.  No incidents with catastrophic potential have been reported during the previous five years.             \n\n*Five Years Accident History:  We have not experienced any reportable accident involving ammonia as defined by 40 CFR 68.42 during the last five (5) years.\n\n*Emergency Response Program:  Cerveceria India, Inc., has developed and emergency action plan to respond to minor fires and spills and for a safe"
    },
    {
      "ESSeqNum": 1,
      "FacilityID": 38777,
      "SummaryText": "plant evacuation.  Cerveceria India, Inc. has coordinated emergency response through a private contractor specialized in response for this type of emergencies.  Cerveceria India, Inc. is actually participating in the LEPC meetings and is committed to contribute to this program."
    }
  ]
